==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}
A [[soil]] variety typically found in [[arid]] climates, usually with little [[leach|leaching]] and minimal [[humus]] content. Referred to as an "Aridisol" in the nomenclature of the United States Department of Agriculture's Natural Resources Conservation Service.

